### 4. Get Candidate Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/candidate/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Test with Invalid Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/candidate/profile
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

### 6. Test without Authorization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/candidate/profile

### 7. Test with Wrong Role (if you have an employer token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/candidate/profile
Authorization: Bearer employer_token_here

### Notes:
# 1. Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT token for a candidate user
# 2. For resume upload, you need an actual PDF file in the same directory
# 3. The API supports both resume upload + AI extraction and manual profile creation
# 4. All dates should be in YYYY-MM-DD format
# 5. Employment types must be one of: full_time, part_time, contract, internship, freelance, volunteer
# 6. Skills proficiency is on a scale of 0-100
